{"tid":347810,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個遇上閪腦細嘅經歷","createTime":"2017-08-05T06:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T10:03:38.000Z","uid":49524,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e030c4db4fd5861eefa421ee21aacd7c674aacc","tid":347810,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"個次見份暑期工 個濕鳩老細in我<br />\n佢其中有一條問題係問我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你覺得打一份工有咩準則？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「其實份份工都唔同嘅...」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話音未落 佢就即刻搏咀<br />\n「唔好講份份工都唔同 講下你以前返嘅工」<br />\n<br />\n我呆左一呆 之後就逐份工數俾佢聽啦<br />\n我數第一份工未講完 佢就話「錯」<br />\n好 數第二份工 佢又話「錯」<br />\n已經燥燥地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 野都唔俾人講埋先<br />\n數第三份工 「錯」<br />\n<br />\n我深吸左啖氣 忍住道氣問佢「咁不如你指教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做野經驗唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n佢第一句就答我<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「其實份份工都唔同嘅」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df788b14abf4d0b07f955f673642db89e6c9738","tid":347810,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"其實係另一個post share 過<br />\n不過今次想集中聽啲閪老闆嘅事"},{"pid":"1a7ee8986617779b88d6d8395169e6219ee41097","tid":347810,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9a287ce738df4f0872b1b82c0f319bf4bf80f189","tid":347810,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"N年前暑期工做物流+裝修<br />\n由原本一個好老闆，經過寫字樓d pk洗腦，變到一個閪老闆，成日恰鳩幫佢做物流裝修既師傅褔利<br />\n<br />\n有一位師傅成日頂老闆嘴，佢就叫寫字樓針對佢隊車隊，將港九新界d物流單打散叫佢送，搞到我做暑期工既日日7，8點都未收得工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc02eceb1861097d38dcf5111e4cb10441ab7f2a","t